Class ProviderTypeController

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.medicaid.controllers.admin.BaseServiceAdminController
      • gov.medicaid.controllers.admin.ProviderTypeController

  • public class ProviderTypeController
extends BaseServiceAdminController

    This controller class that manages a provider type.

    This class is mutable and not thread safe, but used in thread safe manner by framework.
